metadata.name: Tracks
metadata.description:
Getting out to the Ice Shacks can often be a challenge, especially when the snow is deep. Lucky for me, there are usually snowmobile tracks criss-crossing all over the place, and they make a perfect track for me to ski on. 
It often feels like I can jump on a track like this and go on forever, as they head off far into the void. 
If you look closely at this image you'll see a couple Ice Shacks in the distance, and a snowmobile parked next to one of them.
